      "author_alias": "bigalboyo",
      "developer_response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "951963221116177",
      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "Don’t get this or the actual game",
      "review_description": "I would seriously give this 0 stars if I could. The game is so horrendous and full of paywalls that many if not most players buy add-ons for the game just for certain weapons. This “free” version is terrible too. I actually only got about an hour of playtime before I realized that as a free player, you can’t use and weapon above the second tier rarity, and you can’t access 75% of the levels and are locked on the first one. Also, buying the actual game costs 20 dollars, but there are items locked behind 10 dollar paywalls that if you wanted to get access to all weapons, you would be paying 70 dollars. Also, this game is a direct and much worse and more expensive version of Ancient dungeon. Do not buy this game, or the “free” version, or anything about it. This “free” version wasn’t’t even close to a demo, only a sad, messy, and horrible glimpse of the actual game (which isn’t much better)",
      "date": 1772853103,
      "review_helpful_count": 135,
      "author_display_name": "savagelizard789",
      "author_alias": "savagelizard789",
      "developer_response": null
